<Layout title="Eliza's First Birthday">
	<main>
		<h1>Eliza's First Birthday</h1>
		<p>They grow up so fast! It seems like just last week that Eliza was born. Now she's turning one! We're so excited to celebrate with you. Please join us for a fun-filled day of food, friends, and family.</p>
		
		<h2>When?</h2>
		<p>
			<strong>Date: </strong>
			Saturday, October 7th, 2023
			<br/>
			<strong>Time: </strong>
			1:00pm - 4:00pm
		</p>
		
		<h2>Where?</h2>
		<address>
			Alstede Farms<br/>
			1 Alstede Farms Ln<br />
		  Chester, NJ 07930
		</address>
		<p style="margin-bottom: 1rem">
			<a href="https://www.alstedefarms.com/" target="_blank">
				Visit their Website
			</a>
		</p>
		<p>
			<a 
				href="https://www.google.com/maps/place/Alstede+Farms/@40.779056,-74.713821,14z/data=!4m6!3m5!1s0x89c3990b3264ed17:0xd043541046a9664f!8m2!3d40.7789241!4d-74.7137164!16s%2Fg%2F1td7_0ft?hl=en-US&entry=ttu"
				target="_blank"
			>
				Get Directions
			</a>
		</p>

		<h3>Parking and Tent Location</h3>
		<p style="margin-bottom: 0;">Guests must park in the main parking lot behind the farm store.</p>
		<p>Look for us in tent <strong>PEACOCK</strong>.</p>
		
		<h2>What can we bring?</h2>
		<p>
			Please refrain from buying or giving presents. She's perfectly happy with what she has. However, if you're inclined, please consider contributing to <a href="https://accounts.franklintempleton.com/investor/college/-1lYU" target="_blank">Eliza's college fund</a>, or consider donating to <a href="/donate">one of these charities</a>.
		</p>

		<h2>Agenda</h2>

		<ul style="margin-bottom: 0;">
			<li>1:00pm: Hello & Hugs!</li>
			<li>1:30pm: Wagon Departs!*</li>
			<li>2:30pm: Lunch</li>
			<li>3:15pm: Happy Birthday Desserts</li>
			<li>3:45pm: Goodie Bags & Good Byes</li>
		</ul>
		<p style="margin-bottom: 1.5rem">* The wagon will bring us to the fields for fruit picking, but it is completely optional.</p>
		<p>Other activities on the farm include visiting the animals, or you can checkout out the shop for fresh yummies.</p>

		<h3>A Note on Rain</h3>
		<p>It is expected to rain for the duration of the party, but we plan to proceed regardless. We have a tent for hanging out and eating, and the wagon to the fruit picking is covered. We will provide rain ponchos to those of you coming to the fields. Nonetheless, it may be wise to bring a raincoat/umbrella (and extra socks)!</p>

		<h2>Food</h2>
		<p style="margin-bottom: 0">The following food will be provided for lunch:</p>
		<ul style="margin-bottom: 1rem">
			<li>Penne Vodka</li>
			<li>Gluten Free Penne Vodka</li>
			<li>Sausage & Peppers (Gluten Free)</li>
			<li>Pizza</li>
		</ul>
		<p>There will also be veggie platters and dip.</p>

		<h2>What else should we know?</h2>
		<ul>
			<li>The venue is outside, under a tent, so dress appropriately.</li>
			<li>Wear comfortable walking shoes, especially if you plan to come fruit picking.</li>
			<li>No alcohol is allowed on site.</li>
		</ul>
	</main>
</Layout>

